Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.05,0:02:50.14,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,That sound could wake even the dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.40,0:02:59.27,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.20,0:03:06.16,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,How is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.25,0:03:11.90,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a nice flavor.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.90,0:03:13.86,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it's delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.03,0:03:17.54,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's average, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.54,0:03:19.00,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,That's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.42,0:03:22.28,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a special dish from my village.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.28,0:03:26.93,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this "miso" made the same way as soy sauce?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.93,0:03:27.95,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.95,0:03:30.93,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I brought a bit of the miso my mom made.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.93,0:03:35.53,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,There's still a lot more, so don't hold back and eat up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.29,0:03:42.09,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to Treize?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.09,0:03:42.79,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.30,0:03:46.11,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I've finally received notice that supplies are arriving.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.67,0:03:50.79,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Kureha-chan and I are going to pick them up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.18,0:03:54.06,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Munitions, medicine, and other necessities.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.06,0:03:56.10,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,We're running low, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.74,0:03:58.94,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll finally be able to restock them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.48,0:04:00.32,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,And you, Noel?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.95,0:04:02.95,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,She's going to Carl-san's workshop, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.95,0:04:03.97,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.97,0:04:04.93,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.64,0:04:06.31,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanata!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.16,0:04:10.22,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll spend the afternoon practicing the trumpet!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.86,0:04:13.35,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.99,0:04:49.83,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Our meals.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.83,0:04:51.09,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,My...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.40,0:04:53.02,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are your manners?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.62,0:04:56.03,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,If your dad saw this, he'd cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.82,0:05:00.37,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,See if I care.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.01,0:05:11.61,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, have some tea-cakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.37,0:05:16.29,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Fortune Rice Crackers?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.63,0:05:18.68,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,You still hate them, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.37,0:05:22.17,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Those children from the church are innocent, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.81,0:05:28.93,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Raising money by imbuing useless superstitions... They're all the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.51,0:05:32.56,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that's not necessarily true.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.56,0:05:34.52,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,These crackers really are delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.77,0:05:39.60,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.21,0:05:51.62,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,But Kana-chan seems to have adapted to living here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.08,0:05:54.95,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,She works so hard it's adorable.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.95,0:05:56.34,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.34,0:05:59.34,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I do acknowledge her passion and seriousness,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.80,0:06:03.58,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,but I'm not so naive as to think everything will just work out.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.50,0:06:08.99,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with that look?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.98,0:06:11.34,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.11,0:06:16.68,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever. You're getting on my nerves.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.75,0:06:28.59,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be going, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.19,0:06:31.26,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,We might come back later tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.76,0:06:32.50,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.85,0:06:33.85,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.25,0:06:38.46,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't trouble Rio-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.46,0:06:39.25,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.67,0:06:41.02,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Proceeding to depart.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.11,0:06:47.34,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Have a safe trip!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.45,0:06:58.74,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't expect you to do that yet,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.74,0:07:02.15,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,but controlling the notes with the mouthpiece is essential.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.78,0:07:03.85,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Try it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.65,0:07:09.81,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.26,0:07:17.84,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,How do you like living at the base?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.39,0:07:19.76,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.89,0:07:23.13,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,You seem to be enjoying yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.13,0:07:26.03,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a bit jealous of your relaxed temperament.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.83,0:07:33.93,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that I think of it, why did you join the military?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.40,0:07:36.99,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,That's, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.57,0:07:40.56,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that I could learn to play instruments for free...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.49,0:07:43.41,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! But, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.85,0:07:47.01,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I think protecting our country is important, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.41,0:07:49.02,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.02,0:07:51.95,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Whether it's for money or something else,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.95,0:07:57.58,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Those who know what they want tend to last longer here than those who don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.65,0:07:59.66,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.43,0:08:01.95,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm grateful.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.12,0:08:06.83,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,So, how about you, Rio-senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.53,0:08:09.89,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.56,0:08:11.46,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.46,0:08:14.04,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the complete opposite of you, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.45,0:08:18.52,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's really rare these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.52,0:08:22.97,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Especially brass. You hardly hear it outside of the military.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.86,0:08:26.31,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard it a long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.47,0:08:30.19,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Just... Like your...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.19,0:08:30.99,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanata?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.27,0:08:34.78,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Sound... Of the sky...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.42,0:08:45.54,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong? Get yourself together!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.54,0:08:46.59,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, Kanata!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.07,0:08:50.88,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Talk to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.18,0:09:01.56,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.69,0:09:06.04,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, stay still.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.04,0:09:07.44,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,It's hot...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.77,0:09:10.94,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,It's hot, mommy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.94,0:09:12.46,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.46,0:09:16.15,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. It's okay, it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.37,0:09:24.83,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Mom-
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.56,0:09:27.32,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Mommy...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.54,0:09:31.09,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Kanata?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.43,0:09:34.67,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanata!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.72,0:09:39.38,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to eat some snow...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.38,0:09:40.16,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.03,0:09:43.43,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, wait for a bit!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.44,0:09:53.06,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Snow, snow, where's the snow-
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.06,0:09:53.78,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.45,0:09:56.25,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Like hell I'd find it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.94,0:10:01.96,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down... Calm down...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.91,0:10:04.83,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,The medicine!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.45,0:10:15.49,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's the last resort!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.03,0:10:23.09,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Medicine... Medicine...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.03,0:10:26.69,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Medicine! Where's the medicine?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.87,0:10:28.87,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Found it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.77,0:10:33.09,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We're running low, right?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.12,0:10:38.10,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Those Logistics idiots!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.44,0:10:43.36,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit! What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.41,0:10:46.81,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,What should I...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.44,0:11:05.06,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,DAMMIT!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.77,0:12:01.31,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.18,0:12:04.37,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there something I can help you with?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.37,0:12:07.63,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Did the kids give you trouble again?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.77,0:12:11.95,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I apologize for having been so rude.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.95,0:12:13.50,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,So, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.81,0:12:16.36,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I need your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.60,0:12:29.54,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Drink this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.08,0:12:31.82,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Good girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.20,0:12:41.60,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Her fever's quite high,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.60,0:12:43.23,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,but this should bring it down.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.23,0:12:45.81,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Is her illness serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.64,0:12:49.53,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I think it's tertian malaria.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.53,0:12:50.98,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Malaria?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.98,0:12:52.29,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't kids get that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.16,0:12:57.81,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Even adults can get it if they are overworked and exhausted.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.19,0:13:05.80,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Kids often get it right after they come to our church.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.85,0:13:10.56,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,They seem absolutely fine, but suddenly develop a high fever.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.56,0:13:14.57,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,She must have endured it the whole time, I'm sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.57,0:13:16.06,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,T-Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.49,0:13:18.78,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Will she recover?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.78,0:13:20.07,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,She won't die, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.75,0:13:22.82,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I think she'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.91,0:13:28.57,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.18,0:13:34.00,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank... you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.21,0:13:36.58,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.75,0:13:40.09,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Yumina.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.86,0:13:47.66,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a tea made from medicinal herbs.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.24,0:13:51.10,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Please have her drink it again later.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.07,0:13:58.16,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... I apologize for everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.60,0:14:00.94,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.94,0:14:06.45,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Serving the people of this town is our duty, and our joy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.31,0:14:11.63,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,May all of you be blessed with great happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.21,0:14:18.29,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I thank you for your assistance.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.11,0:16:18.20,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.69,0:16:23.00,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Feeling better?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.27,0:16:26.46,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.60,0:16:37.20,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a miso.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.20,0:16:39.27,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm? From this morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.27,0:16:40.72,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.72,0:16:45.62,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,The bean lees. When you make the soup, you filter the miso.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.13,0:16:48.73,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the bean lees left in the filter.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.31,0:16:52.53,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,They're called "leftovers" or "hindrances,"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.53,0:16:53.99,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,like me...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.55,0:16:57.70,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,That's how I've been, ever since I was little.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.70,0:16:58.49,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.18,0:17:04.25,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I told myself I'd do my best and not be a burden to everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.09,0:17:06.07,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Even so...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.86,0:17:12.62,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,You're more delicate than you look, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.18,0:17:16.22,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Selfish and spoiled, at that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.79,0:17:23.43,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Did I say anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.88,0:17:25.52,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Lots of things.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.03,0:17:36.83,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.50,0:17:39.27,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.27,0:17:41.56,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,The song you just sang...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.56,0:17:44.49,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.01,0:17:46.58,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,This song.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.48,0:18:03.36,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,That's surprising,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.36,0:18:05.40,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,you heard it just once.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.40,0:18:06.77,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Not just once.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.26,0:18:11.23,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard it a long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.07,0:18:15.19,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,150)}I wished I was able to play that song myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.36,0:18:17.97,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.71,0:18:23.49,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to play the song that resounds from the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.19,0:18:30.79,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,But, I guess a miso will be a miso wherever it goes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.50,0:18:32.32,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanata.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.47,0:18:37.80,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't rely on the church all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.70,0:18:42.10,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,The Takemikazuchi is a relic from a past era.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.10,0:18:46.19,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,And lots of things are hidden inside it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.19,0:18:47.52,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Lots of things?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.52,0:18:48.55,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.55,0:18:51.06,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Ask Noel about the details later.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.09,0:19:06.53,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, this'll do.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.22,0:19:08.04,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,It's starting!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.84,0:19:22.04,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,This... This song-
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.11,0:20:03.86,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,This is probably the complete form of the song.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.32,0:20:08.54,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Various instruments, each resounding their parts,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.54,0:20:10.35,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,combining into a song.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.46,0:20:12.93,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just like operating a tank.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.82,0:20:19.52,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,The commander, gunner, driver, and signaller.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.52,0:20:23.12,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone combines their ability to move a single tank.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.86,0:20:25.51,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody's useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.45,0:20:29.37,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no note that isn't necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.20,0:20:37.25,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't look at me like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.25,0:20:38.38,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Those aren't my words.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.00,0:20:43.39,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,They're from the one I adore, and look up to the most.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.03,0:20:46.60,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to borrow her words...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.60,0:20:51.10,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanata, for what reason do you think seniors exist?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.09,0:20:55.36,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so they can be troubled by their juniors.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.98,0:20:59.61,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine if you can't do it right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.08,0:21:02.77,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Just remember the feelings of frustration and helplessness,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.77,0:21:05.51,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,and the feeling of happiness when you were protected.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.85,0:21:12.46,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be useful when it's your turn to protect, someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.29,0:21:17.66,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,So, go ahead and be as troublesome as you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.66,0:21:19.38,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I did myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.46,0:21:24.48,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, you'll be scolded when you make mistakes. And you'll be punished.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.48,0:21:28.39,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,But, tell me if you're hurt, or suffering.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.17,0:21:31.20,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.12,0:21:38.55,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.55,0:21:42.48,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make sure I cause you a {\i1}lot{\i0} of trouble from now on!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.47,0:21:44.48,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No, I meant...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.68,0:21:51.90,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Restrain yourself a bit, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.13,0:21:59.12,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, jeez! I knew I should have stayed back after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.51,0:22:03.88,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe Kanata made Rio-senpai nurse her...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.15,0:22:06.84,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you saying? It wasn't a big deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.37,0:22:09.01,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,She was just worn out, it seems.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.63,0:22:10.88,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Just needs a little rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.45,0:22:19.03,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,The Takemikazuchi was on.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.60,0:22:23.32,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, sorry. I used it for a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.32,0:22:25.37,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Was there a problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.37,0:22:26.15,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.50,0:22:28.67,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,So you listened to that song?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.19,0:22:30.78,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.98,0:22:34.65,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,But you said you'd never listen to it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.66,0:22:37.29,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I just felt like it, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.00,0:22:41.00,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,And then?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.76,0:22:44.13,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.10,0:24:19.93,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Next episode: Sky of the Rainy Season - Quartz Rainbow
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.85,0:00:18.24,OP-TL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2.2\fad(130,130)}The radiance of this sky will carry to your heart
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.84,0:00:28.55,OP-TL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2.2\fad(130,130)}The melody you dreamed of is like serenity
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.55,0:00:33.54,OP-TL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2.2\fad(130,130)}For your hands the dream is still far away, but
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.54,0:00:38.54,OP-TL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2.2\fad(130,130)}remember the voice so gentle
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.55,0:00:51.23,OP-TL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2.2\fad(130,130)}when someone sang the chord of happiness
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.26,0:01:00.70,OP-TL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2.2\fad(130,130)}The sound of the skies echoes high over all sadness
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.70,0:01:11.34,OP-TL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2.2\fad(130,130)}Everything reflected in your eyes is the real world
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.34,0:01:20.68,OP-TL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2.2\fad(130,130)}Not even the shedding of of tears can stop you here
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.68,0:01:33.24,OP-TL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2.2\fad(130,130)}We're playing tomorrow in the light that rains without end
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.43,0:22:51.22,ED-TL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}Pile up the feelings of love and friendship
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.22,0:22:54.31,ED-TL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}Performing is also important
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.70,0:23:12.31,ED-TL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}I cried happily
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.45,0:23:18.26,ED-TL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}I laughed eagerly
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.72,0:23:27.57,ED-TL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}But all of them make me alive
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.57,0:23:31.71,ED-TL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}Let's walk slowly
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.71,0:23:33.56,ED-TL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}Everybody singing
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.56,0:23:37.66,ED-TL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}Tell me why we dance
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.66,0:23:38.93,ED-TL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}You just my friend
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.93,0:23:45.09,ED-TL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}Even if love and friendship change over time
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.09,0:23:50.55,ED-TL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}I want them to echo forever
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.09,0:23:56.87,ED-TL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}Speaking endless words touched by love
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.87,0:24:03.01,ED-TL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}Our harmony
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.03,0:24:07.64,ED-TL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}I can hear our harmony
